\[\big{|}\nabla e^{\Delta}f\big{|}(o)=\left|\int\limits_{\mathbb{H}^{1}}\nabla p \big{(}g^{-1}\big{)}\big{(}f(g)-f_{o}\big{)}\,dg\right|\leqslant\int\limits_{ \mathbb{H}^{1}}\big{|}\nabla p\big{(}g^{-1}\big{)}\big{|}\cdot\big{|}f(g)-f_{o} \big{|}\,dg.\]

