\[\det D\Phi_{i}(x,\theta)=R_{1}+R_{2}. \tag{4.18}\]_Calcul de \(R_{1}\)._ Puisque la premiere colonne de \(R_{1}^{*}\) peut s'ecrire comme

\[\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\left(\begin{array}{c}K_{1}\\ -K_{2}\end{array}\right)+\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{1}}\left(\begin{array} []{c}dx_{1}(i)/ds(i)\\ dx_{2}(i)/ds(i)\end{array}\right),\]

